Articles.Content:
I have corrupted my ksp by installing these 2 mods: [https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/344](https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/344) and [http://kerbal.curseforge.com/ksp-mods/223941-vens-part-revamp](http://kerbal.curseforge.com/ksp-mods/223941-vens-part-revamp)

and now the parts list will not even show the parts and it also says that my ships have incompatible parts and can not load them. If any of you know how to fix this please tell me.
It's Ven's Stock Part Revamp. It removes some of the stock parts and replaces them with revamped ones.
